title: Chinese spacecraft Shenzhou-8 disengages from space lab module Tiangong-1
description: BEIJING， Nov. 14 (Xinhua) -- China's Shenzhou-8 unmanned spacecraft successfully disengaged from the space lab module Tiangong-1 Monday evening after a 12-day flight together， according to the mission's control center.
